name: MOON WAVE TREASURY
description: MOON WAVE is twin-token project on ERC20 and BSC. MOON WAVE on ERC20 auto rewards in USTC while simultaneously auto-burning USTC. MOON WAVE on BSC auto rewards in LUNC while simultaneously auto-burning LUNC. The ultimate goal of the project is to repeg USTC to the dollar so that it is a stable coin once-again. Doing this serves as a quadruple utility for the project. The auto-rewards in LUNC and USTC as well as the auto-burn of both. This treasury will serve to not only pump the chart of the project on both chains, but it will also serve as a source of funding for future development of the project.
